highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Canada. “Golden” is the highest at #5.
“One Last Breath - Remix” by ATLiens has been on Viral Songs Canada the longest, at 89 days straight.
“Runaway (U & I)” by Ian Asher and Galantis is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Canada, up 18 spots at #74.
“The Best” by Petric is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Canada at #94.
